						<h2 style="text-align:left"><font size="7">Media Coverage</font></h2>
                                         
<p style="text-align:justify"><font size="4">Astrobiology has a wide-ranging media appeal. Everything from the discovery of the latest far-flung Earth-like
 world to the telltale signs of past water flows in ancient rocks on Mars gains television and radio coverage,
as well as coverage in written publications, ranging from daily and online newspapers to specialist science
magazines.</font></p>
</br>
</br>

