<p style="text-align:left"><font size="4">Fox News (April, 2011): <a "href="http://www.foxnews.com/scitech/2011/04/19/black-trees-blossom-world-suns/">Could Black Trees Blossom on a World With Two Suns?</a></font></p>

<p style="text-align:left"><font size="4">Wired (March, 2012): <a href="http://www.wired.com/2012/03/why-black-or-blue-or-red-plants-might-be-the-key-to-finding-life-beyond-earth/">Why Black (or Blue, or Red) Plants Might Be the Key to Finding Life Beyond Earth</a></font></p>

