<p style="text-align:left"><font size="4">New Scientist (October 2013): <a href="http://www.newscientist.com/article/dn24490-exoplanet-hunters-may-find-et-by-glut-of-alien-corpses.html#.U-4FZ3Wx3UZ">Exoplanet Hunters May Find ET By Glut of Alien Corpses</a></font></p>

<p style="text-align:left"><font size="4">National Geographic (October 2013): <a href="http://news.nationalgeographic.com/news/2013/10/131028-earth-biosignature-doomsday-space-science/">Study: Sun Will End Earthly Life in 2.8 Billion Years</a></font></p>

